20:48.614 --> 20:51.276
- Can I have this spotlight dance?
- What?

20:51.383 --> 20:54.580
- I tipped the pilot to hover!
- I can't hearwhatyou're-

20:54.686 --> 20:57.655
Dance with me, my queen!

